

1. Restart policies


2. how to restart docker deamon?
systemctl restart docker

3. removed container 
docker rm COntainerName ( docker rm -f - if you want to force remove)

4. how to check space 
df -h

5. how to check docker space and usaged 

docker system df -h
6 . how to check docker space and usaged based on size
docker system df -h

7. automatic dellete container  after job done
docker container run -dt -rm --name testcontainer InageNmae pin -c10 google.com
--see docker ps
- see docker logs testcontainer
-- see docker ps ( it should not be runing )

8. how to see layer of image
docker history ImageName

9. how to inspect images
docker image inspect nginx --format='{{.ContainerConfig.Hostname}}'
docker image inspect nginx | grep Hostname

10. remove all unused iamges
docker image prune -a






